| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3423 — Recovery Inhibition (ragnarlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 860aee92-5ddf-5cbc-b6b0-a89e45e72abf"
